{"tid":1086634,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[神奇力量] 波圖大將離奇重創　歐聯益晒利物浦","createTime":"2019-04-01T01:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T03:26:42.000Z","uid":31798,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"401a8462a430b83a735987d79feb25e3875d4bfa","tid":1086634,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:39:44.000Z","msg":"利物浦本季挑戰英超冠軍，於歐聯亦已殺入8強抽正波圖，好多球迷都覺得係支好籤，依家波圖仲有主力左閘阿歷士迪尼斯離奇受傷，呢支葡萄牙勁旅認真黑仔！呢名剛為巴西踢熱身賽對巴拿馬嘅森巴國腳，主射12碼時疑似用力過猛，自己拉傷右面Pat Pat位置，即時要被調離火線，咁樣拉親睇嚟要休息一段時間，對紅軍嘅8強首回合，甚至係兩回合都未必出得。<br />\n<br />\n26歲嘅阿歷士迪尼斯係波圖正選大將，今輪葡超作客布拉加，波圖下半場初段仲係輸緊1:2，之後波圖得到12碼，阿歷士迪尼斯左腳勁射搞掂，但佢隨即撳住右邊Pat Pat附近位置痛極倒地，之後即時要被換走。<br />\n<br />\n歐聯8強首回合，將於香港時間4月10號上演，離依家只係淨番個零星期，波圖冇咗呢位正選壓陣的話，慣於右路搵食嘅穆罕默德沙拿，肯定會比較好踢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190331/bkn-20190331210035940-0331_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190331%2Fbkn-20190331210035940-0331_00882_001.html&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j4CLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=68cb894c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190331/bkn-20190331210035940-0331_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c5aa6e6e161c9ef66b52f5f9e5866e2d9b22d8a","tid":1086634,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"假波好時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58d02b972c40f318021f6551cad309a4c3d01b8","tid":1086634,"uid":162906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"重注買利物浦喇."},{"pid":"a1f170fe1c661d5c5c039f0b4fe391b7d921135c","tid":1086634,"uid":8219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:55:10.000Z","msg":"all in馬賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ffee4c73af8deefc3a7eae50da